  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Echo Seed Detection Device",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "回音种子侦测设备",
    "TraditionalChinese": "回音種子偵測裝置"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "An attachment for the Multi-Tool <span class=\"name name-technology\">Scanner</span>, designed by Specialist Polo for the detection of atlantideum-infused <span class=\"name name-special\">sentience echoes</span>.<br><br>On <span class=\"name name-special\">dissonant</span> worlds, use the Analysis Visor (<span class=\"name name-img\">AIM</span>) to locate sentience echoes. On arrival at an echo site, use <span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span> to <span class=\"name name-special\">fully reveal</span> nearby anomalies.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "多用途工具<span class=\"name name-technology\">扫描仪</span>配件，由保罗专家为实现侦测与亚特拉迪姆融合的<span class=\"name name-special\">智慧回音</span>的目的而专门设计。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-special\">不谐</span>世界上使用分析面甲（<span class=\"name name-img\">AIM</span>）定位智慧回音。抵达回音地点后，使用<span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span><span class=\"name name-special\">完全揭示</span>周遭异象。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "工具組的附屬<span class=\"name name-technology\">掃描器</span>，由專家波羅所設計，用於偵測注入亞特蘭提德鋼的<span class=\"name name-special\">智慧生物回音</span>。<br><br>身處<span class=\"name name-special\">不和諧</span>世界時，使用分析護目鏡 (<span class=\"name name-img\">AIM</span>) 即可找到智慧生物回音。到達回音地點後，使用 <span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span> 即可<span class=\"name name-special\">完全揭示</span>附近的異常。"
  },
